Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.95,0:02:15.11,D,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's the match
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.09,0:02:17.55,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucky shot
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.21,0:02:20.93,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Well done, Miss Nikos
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.93,0:02:23.62,D,,0000,0000,0000,,You should have no problem qualifying for the tournament
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.62,0:02:25.09,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, professor
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.42,0:02:26.22,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.22,0:02:30.13,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I know that's a tough act to follow, but we have time for one more sparring match
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.13,0:02:31.56,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Any volunteers?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.03,0:02:34.20,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Belladonna?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.00,0:02:38.31,D,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been rather docile for the past few classes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.31,0:02:38.87,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.87,0:02:39.83,D,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.37,0:02:42.80,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Mercury, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.08,0:02:44.16,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.16,0:02:45.67,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's find you an opponent
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.67,0:02:46.65,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.25,0:02:49.96,D,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna fight..her
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.66,0:02:51.75,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.75,0:02:54.02,D,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid Miss Nikos has just finished the match
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.02,0:02:56.27,D,,0000,0000,0000,,I recommend you choose another partner
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.27,0:02:57.72,D,,0000,0000,0000,,No! it's fine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.02,0:03:00.99,D,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be happy to oblige
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.39,0:03:54.28,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, your friend's doing pretty good
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.42,0:04:20.47,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Humm..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.58,0:04:28.61,D,,0000,0000,0000,,I forfeit
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.78,0:04:32.51,D,,0000,0000,0000,,You..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.24,0:04:35.30,D,,0000,0000,0000,,..don't even want to try?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.68,0:04:36.68,D,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the point?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.68,0:04:39.39,D,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a world-renowned fighter, we're obviously leagues apart
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.33,0:04:41.82,D,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.82,0:04:45.79,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Pyrrha Nikos is the victor of the match..again
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.23,0:04:51.93,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time you may want to think a little harder before choosing an opponent
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.67,0:04:53.97,D,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be sure to do that
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.07,0:04:57.44,D,,0000,0000,0000,,That is all for today
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.19,0:05:00.42,D,,0000,0000,0000,,And remember, the dance is this weekend
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.42,0:05:03.01,D,,0000,0000,0000,,But you all have your first mission on Monday
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.28,0:05:05.91,D,,0000,0000,0000,,I will not accept any excuses
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.79,0:05:15.82,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Learning is so much fun
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.87,0:05:25.73,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Blake!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.73,0:05:27.54,D,,0000,0000,0000,,You uh..doing okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.54,0:05:28.64,D,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.80,0:05:32.67,D,,0000,0000,0000,,So I hear there's this dance going on this weekend..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.67,0:05:34.65,D,,0000,0000,0000,,and sounds pretty lame, but..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.65,0:05:36.91,D,,0000,0000,0000,,you and me, I'm thinking, not as lame, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.26,0:05:38.08,D,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.08,0:05:41.18,D,,0000,0000,0000,,The dance! This weekend! You wanna go, or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.18,0:05:43.42,D,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time for a stupid dance
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.42,0:05:45.95,D,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you of all people would get that
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.88,0:05:53.21,D,,0000,0000,0000,,You what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.21,0:05:55.18,D,,0000,0000,0000,,We want you to go to the dance
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.18,0:05:56.52,D,,0000,0000,0000,,That's ridiculous
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.52,0:05:58.00,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Blake, we're worried about you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.00,0:06:00.34,D,,0000,0000,0000,,This investigation is starting to mess with your head
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.34,0:06:02.64,D,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't sleep, you hardly eat
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.64,0:06:04.97,D,,0000,0000,0000,,And to be honest, your grades have been suffering
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.97,0:06:08.21,D,,0000,0000,0000,,You think I care about grades? People's lives are at stake!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.58,0:06:12.05,D,,0000,0000,0000,,We know, and we're also trying to figure out what Torchwick is up to
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.05,0:06:16.34,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you and Sun, we know they're operating somewhere outside of southeast Vale
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.34,0:06:22.82,D,,0000,0000,0000,,And, the Schnee company records singled out Vale as the primary target for Dust robberies over the last few months
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.82,0:06:24.99,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget about their missing military tech too
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.99,0:06:27.25,D,,0000,0000,0000,,But there're still unanswered questions!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.25,0:06:31.33,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Blake, you won't be able to find anything if you can't even keep your eyes open
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.33,0:06:34.64,D,,0000,0000,0000,,All we're asking is that you take it easy for one day
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.64,0:06:37.64,D,,0000,0000,0000,,It will be fun! Yang and I will make sure of it
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.64,0:06:39.74,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! We're planning the whole event!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.74,0:06:40.81,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.81,0:06:43.52,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Team CFVY's away mission lasted longer than expected
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.52,0:06:45.82,D,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Weiss and I were asked to pick up where they left off
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.08,0:06:48.40,D,,0000,0000,0000,,And now we can make sure you have the perfect night
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.40,0:06:52.22,D,,0000,0000,0000,,And once it's all over, we'll return to our search, rested and ready
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.52,0:06:53.99,D,,0000,0000,0000,,So..what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.79,0:06:59.49,D,,0000,0000,0000,,I think this is a colossal waste of time
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.57,0:07:06.77,D,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be in the library
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.17,0:07:12.15,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Great
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.15,0:07:14.24,D,,0000,0000,0000,,She can't keep going like this
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.99,0:07:26.59,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Weiss~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.59,0:07:33.10,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.05,0:07:35.60,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Open the door..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.97,0:07:39.27,D,,0000,0000,0000,,I promise not to sing
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.86,0:07:44.71,D,,0000,0000,0000,,I lied!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.71,0:07:47.04,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Weiss Schnee
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.48,0:07:49.41,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you accompany me
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.01,0:07:52.38,D,,0000,0000,0000,,to the dance on..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.80,0:07:55.65,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Sunday
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.02,0:07:58.85,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you done?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.32,0:08:01.09,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.02,0:08:02.76,D,,0000,0000,0000,,No
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.63,0:08:05.43,D,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.43,0:08:08.30,D,,0000,0000,0000,,And that is why they call you the Ice Queen
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.30,0:08:11.90,D,,0000,0000,0000,,All my life, boys have only cared about the perks of my last name
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.90,0:08:13.12,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.12,0:08:15.10,D,,0000,0000,0000,,I already have a date in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.10,0:08:16.62,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Date or no date
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.62,0:08:19.21,D,,0000,0000,0000,,None of this will matter if we can't get Blake to go
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.49,0:08:38.66,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Well done!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.16,0:08:41.53,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Your swordplay's improved immensely
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.86,0:08:43.26,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't have done it without you
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.73,0:08:44.50,D,,0000,0000,0000,,So
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.00,0:08:46.77,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you ready to move on to Aura?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.54,0:08:51.37,D,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm actually thinking maybe we just skip Aura tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.37,0:08:52.81,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Might go on a jog or something
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.11,0:08:54.24,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.64,0:08:56.61,D,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you get frustrated
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.95,0:08:58.85,D,,0000,0000,0000,,But you must keep trying
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.21,0:09:02.12,D,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure we'll discover your Semblance any day now
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.12,0:09:04.05,D,,0000,0000,0000,,That's..not it
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.75,0:09:05.56,D,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.53,0:09:07.66,D,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dumb
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.19,0:09:09.09,D,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.03,0:09:13.43,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Jaune, you know you can tell me
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.96,0:09:16.50,D,,0000,0000,0000,,It's..Weiss
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.53,0:09:18.13,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.67,0:09:20.64,D,,0000,0000,0000,,What about her?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.14,0:09:24.17,D,,0000,0000,0000,,I asked her to the dance and she shot me down
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.37,0:09:25.50,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Big surprise, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.41,0:09:27.31,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Well
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.01,0:09:30.95,D,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe the saying goes: There's..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.45,0:09:33.28,D,,0000,0000,0000,,plenty of fish in the sea
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.05,0:09:35.42,D,,0000,0000,0000,,That's easy for you to say
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.42,0:09:38.55,D,,0000,0000,0000,,You've probably got guys clamoring over each other just to ask you out
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.19,0:09:41.46,D,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd be surprised
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.09,0:09:46.83,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh please. If you don't get a date to the dance, I'll wear a dress
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.83,0:09:47.43,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Heh
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.00,0:09:53.57,D,,0000,0000,0000,,And finally, Pyrrha Nikos
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.57,0:09:56.13,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, the invincible girl
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.13,0:09:57.14,D,,0000,0000,0000,,She's smart
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.74,0:09:59.67,D,,0000,0000,0000,,But I wouldn't say invincible
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.67,0:10:01.28,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Do tell
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.81,0:10:03.61,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Her semblance is Polarity
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.88,0:10:06.20,D,,0000,0000,0000,,But you'd never know just by watching
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.20,0:10:10.05,D,,0000,0000,0000,,After she made contact with my boots, she was able to move them around however she wanted
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.75,0:10:13.08,D,,0000,0000,0000,,But she only made slight adjustments
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.08,0:10:15.72,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Just enough to make it look like she's untouchable
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.09,0:10:20.25,D,,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't broadcast her power, so it puts her opponent at a disadvantage
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.63,0:10:23.10,D,,0000,0000,0000,,People assume she's fated for victory
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.70,0:10:27.30,D,,0000,0000,0000,,When she's really taking fate into her own hands
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.66,0:10:29.74,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.60,0:10:32.01,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Add her to the list
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.56,0:10:36.74,D,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be able to take her no problem
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.06,0:10:39.88,D,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not about overpowering the enemy
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.62,0:10:43.79,D,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about taking away what power they have
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.79,0:10:46.39,D,,0000,0000,0000,,And we will, in time
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.72,0:10:49.99,D,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.53,0:10:52.19,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, Mercury
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.19,0:10:54.93,D,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a fun weekend ahead of us
